{{version025}}
{{flavour|Exhales a large cloud of blessed flame, shining with the glory of the good gods. These flames are especially dangerous to undead and demonic creatures, and have no effect on holy creatures.}}

'''Holy Breath''' is a dangerous monster-only spell that creates [[clouds]] of [[Cloud#Blessed_fire|blessed fire]], inflicting irresistible damage upon characters not worshiping [[good gods]]. The clouds are especially dangerous for [[demonic]] and [[undead]] creatures.

{{monsters with spell}}

==Tips and Tricks==
*The spell cannot affect tiles that already have clouds. So make use of this by reading a [[scroll of fog]] or casting [[Mephitic Cloud]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
